We got a show!
Kookslams new weekly show “Kookslams Friday Funday” is now officially on FUEL TV and available 24/7 on FUEL TV+! 

As a stoker to our community, use VIP promo code “Kook” and get 50% off your yearly subscription to FUEL TV+. 
Simply go to www.fuel.tv , click Try FUEL TV+, & apply your VIP promo code “Kook”. @fuel.tv

node.text:
GIVEAWAY TIME! We teamed up with the legends at @catchsurf and are giving away one 8’ soft top shred sled and a year supply of @kookslamshardseltzer
